title: Nelly Joins Us In Studio to Co-Host the Show!
description: Dave's back from vacation with some fun stories, Nelly joins us in studio and talks all about life, what it takes to be successful, we call a Super Fan and try to convince her Nelly is on the phone, Nelly versus Heidi in the One Note Game, the moment Nelly's grandma was super excited about him being "Nelly" because he got a picture with a certain celeb, and more!
